text: Paso Ancho is a corregimiento in Tierras Altas District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It was established by Law 55 of September 13, 2013.Ley 55 del 13 de septiembre del 2013. ==Climate== Paso Ancho has a subtropical highland climate (Cwb) with moderate to little rainfall from December to April and heavy to very heavy rainfall from May to November. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
title: Paso Ancho
